        <p style="padding-left: 40px; font-size: 16px;">Attorney-in-Fact</p>

        <p style="margin-top:20px;padding-left:40px;">ID No.______________________</p>

        <p style="margin-top:20px;">
            REPUBLIC OF THE PHILIPPINES)<br>
            CITY OF <span style="padding-left:250px;">)</span>
        </p>
